{"lemma":"إِشادَةٌ","slug":"إِشادَةٌ","root":"ش.#.د","root_slug":"ش-_-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-_-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23491"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D8%B4%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23491","headword_ar":"اشادهُ","root":"$yd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 2. ―         -b2-  Hence, (L,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i$aAdapN","text_ar":"اـِشَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raising the voice"},{"kind":"text","text":"in saying a thing (Lth, S, L, K) [of any kind, or] such as one's companion dislikes; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanodiydN","text_ar":"تَنْدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, L.) See also 1. You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$Ad Sawotahu","text_ar":"اشاد صَوْتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biSawotihi","text_ar":"بِصَوْتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised his voice."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$Ad bihi","text_ar":"اشاد بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He proclaimed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cried it, raising his voice;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a stray, or any other thing: (As, L:) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made it known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, S, A,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1630},{"kind":"text","text":"K; *) namely, a stray. (S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$Ad bi*ikorihi","text_ar":"اشاد بِذِكْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised his good fame, by praising him; raised a good report of him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, L:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he raised his ill fame, by dispraising him; raised an evil report of him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$Adhu","text_ar":"اشادهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAdahu","text_ar":"شَادَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he raised his notoriety"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fame."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$Ad Ealayohi","text_ar":"اشاد عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He published against him"},{"kind":"text","text":"something disliked, disapproved, or odious: one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$Ad Ealayohi qabiyHFA","text_ar":"اشاد عَلَيْهِ قَبِيحًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biqabiyHK","text_ar":"بِقَبِيحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He published against him something bad, evil, abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i$aAdapN","text_ar":"اـِشَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)  The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"destroying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) from the same word as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanodiydN","text_ar":"تَنْدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["L","Lth","S","K","As","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}